snippet.title: entertainmentie
snippet.description:
entertainment.ie is Ireland's leading online publication for movies, TV, music, and gaming.

Our YouTube channel features movie, TV, and gaming reviews, interviews with some of the biggest stars in the business, and lots more.

Subscribe here: https://bit.ly/2BfI4hl

Official site: http://entertainment.ie

Follow us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/entertainmentie
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/EntertainmentIE
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/entertainmentie
Follow us on TikTok: @entertainment.ie
